'''伊森·葛特曼'''（{{lang-en|'''Ethan Gutmann'''}}，{{bd|1958年|||}}）是[[美国|美国]][[记者|记者]]、作家。曾对中共摘取[[法轮功|法轮功]]学员[[器官|器官]]问题进行调查，著有《屠殺》（{{lang|en|The Slaughter: Mass Killings, Organ Harvesting, and China's Secret Solution to Its Dissident Problem}}）一书，但於2018年10月2日稱書內內容取材舉證來源[[柯文哲|柯文哲]]是騙子。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2018-10-02/147225|title=被葛特曼說是Liar 柯P怒：不解釋清楚就告！|accessdate=2018-10-02|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2020-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202053109/https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2018-10-02/147225|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[http://www.weeklystandard.com/author/ethan-gutmann "Ethan Gutmann"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.weeklystandard.com/author/ethan-gutmann |date=20190618111200 }}, ''[[The_Weekly_Standard|The Weekly Standard]]</ref>

==早期生活和教育==
葛特曼获得了[[哥伦比亚大学|哥伦比亚大学]]文学[[学士|学士]]学位和国际事务[[硕士|硕士]]学位。

==中共器官摘取==
从2006年起，葛特曼写作关于活摘器官的文章<ref>Ethan Gutmann (8 May 2006) [http://www.weeklystandard.com/Content/Public/Articles/000/000/012/160ymogj.asp? "Why Wang Wenyi Was Shouting"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.weeklystandard.com/Content/Public/Articles/000/000/012/160ymogj.asp |date=20151009111217 }}, ''[[The_Weekly_Standard|The Weekly Standard]]''</ref><ref>Ethan Gutmann (24 November 2008) [http://www.weeklystandard.com/Content/Public/Articles/000/000/015/824qbcjr.asp "China's Gruesome Organ Harvest"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.weeklystandard.com/Content/Public/Articles/000/000/015/824qbcjr.asp |date=20120524133009 }}, ''The Weekly Standard''</ref><ref>[http://www.worldaffairsjournal.org/article/bitter-harvest-china%E2%80%99s-%E2%80%98organ-donation%E2%80%99-nightmare "Bitter Harvest: China's 'Organ Donation' Nightmare"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.worldaffairsjournal.org/article/bitter-harvest-china%E2%80%99s-%E2%80%98organ-donation%E2%80%99-nightmare |date=20150323020421 }}, World Affairs Journal July/August 2012</ref>。2012年，《国家器官：在中国的移植滥用》出版了六篇医疗专业[[论文|论文]]<ref>[http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=Danovitch+G G Danovitch articles] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=Danovitch+G |date=20200202042655 }}, [[US_National_Library_of_Medicine|US National Library of Medicine]]</ref><ref>[http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=Caplan+AL AL Caplan articles] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=Caplan+AL |date=20200202041237 }}, US National Library of Medicine</ref><ref>[http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=Lavee+J J Lavee articles] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=Lavee+J |date=20200202041156 }}, US National Library of Medicine</ref><ref>[http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=Ahmad+G G Ahmad articles] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=Ahmad+G |date=20200202041153 }}, US National Library of Medicine</ref><ref>[http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=Trey+T T Trey articles] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=Trey+T |date=20200202041127 }}, US National Library of Medicine</ref><ref>[http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=Fiatarone+Singh+M M Fiatarone Singh articles] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=Fiatarone+Singh+M |date=20200202041124 }}, US National Library of Medicine</ref>，[[大卫·麦塔斯|大卫·麦塔斯]]与葛特曼采访了100名证人<ref>[http://www.seraphimeditions.com/pdfs/Introduction-State-Organs "State Organs: Introduction"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.seraphimeditions.com/pdfs/Introduction-State-Organs |date=20130527201924 }} seraphimeditions.com</ref><ref>Rebeca Kuropatwa (19 September 2012) [http://www.jewishtribune.ca/arts-and-culture/2012/09/19/new-matas-book-reveals-transplant-abuse "New Matas book reveals transplant abuse"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.jewishtribune.ca/arts-and-culture/2012/09/19/new-matas-book-reveals-transplant-abuse |date=20150402124932 }}, [[Jewish_Tribune_(Canada)|Jewish Tribune (Canada)]]</ref><ref>[[Mark_Colvin|Mark Colvin]] (27 November 2012) [http://www.abc.net.au/pm/content/2012/s3642188.htm "Parliament to hear evidence of transplant abuse in China"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.abc.net.au/pm/content/2012/s3642188.htm |date=20160613183433 }}, ''[[Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation|Australian Broadcasting Corporation]]''</ref><ref>Matthew Robertson (31 August 2012) [http://www.theepochtimes.com/n3/22976-book-exposes-organized-killing-for-organs-in-china "Book Exposes Organized Killing for Organs in China"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.theepochtimes.com/n3/22976-book-exposes-organized-killing-for-organs-in-china |date=20170903012051 }}, ''[[The_Epoch_Times|The Epoch Times]]''</ref><ref>David Matas, Dr. Torsten Trey (2012) [http://www.seraphimeditions.com/state-organs.html State Organs, Transplant Abuse in China] {{Wayback|url=http://www.seraphimeditions.com/state-organs.html |date=20150224121713 }}, seraphimeditions.com p. 144</ref>，包括法轮功的幸存者、医生、警察和[[劳教|劳教所]]管理员。他估计在2000年至2008年間，至少65,000法轮功学员被为获取他们的器官而遭杀害<ref name=Tstar>Barbara Turnbull (21 October 2014)  [http://www.thestar.com/life/2014/10/21/qa_author_and_analyst_ethan_gutmann_discusses_chinas_illegal_organ_trade.html "Q&A: Author and analyst Ethan Gutmann discusses China's illegal organ trade"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.thestar.com/life/2014/10/21/qa_author_and_analyst_ethan_gutmann_discusses_chinas_illegal_organ_trade.html |date=20201101011201 }}, ''[[The_Toronto_Star|The Toronto Star]]''</ref><ref name="Jay">Jay Nordlinger (25 August 2014) [http://www.nationalreview.com/sites/default/files/nordlinger_gutmann08-25-14.html "Face The Slaughter: The Slaughter: Mass Killings, Organ Harvesting, and China's Secret Solution to Its Dissident Problem, by Ethan Gutmann"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nationalreview.com/sites/default/files/nordlinger_gutmann08-25-14.html |date=20160223172904 }}, ''[[National_Review|National Review]]''</ref><ref>Viv Young (11 August 2014) [http://www.nyjournalofbooks.com/book-review/slaughter-mass-killings-organ-harvesting "The Slaughter: Mass Killings, Organ Harvesting, and China's Secret Solution to Its Dissident Problem"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nyjournalofbooks.com/book-review/slaughter-mass-killings-organ-harvesting |date=20151019053030 }}, ''[[New_York_Journal_of_Books|New York Journal of Books]]''</ref>。

